 5) auto incremant:
    -> when we want to apply and filed to start auto incremant without accept value from user it genetate auto
       indexes in field value.
    -> it's start with 1 if you want to start with 10 or 100 you cane just aplly auto_incremant=10
    creation time:

       syntax:
        create table<tablename>
        (
            fieldname <datatype(int)> auto_incremant
        );
